snippet.title: God Will Lift Us Up (Barron Trump Singing)
snippet.description:
God Will Lift Us Up

Check us out on Spotify! https://open.spotify.com/album/3y1CZVxPBVqYl2ljdNVWno?si=lLRWLYbeQcuXD9TQDeKi7A

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Lyrics:
God Will Lift Us Up

They say the storm is coming fast,
Dark clouds above, but it won’t last.
I’ve seen this nation rise before,
With faith and strength, we’ll stand once more.

Through every trial, we hold on tight,
In darkest times, we find the light.
With hands in prayer, our hearts are strong,
God’s guiding us, we can’t go wrong.

God will lift us up again,
Through the fire, through the rain.
Hope’s not lost, we still believe,
America will rise and lead.

I see the future, bright and clear,
A land of promise, free from fear.
With faith in Him, we’ll walk the way,
Tomorrow shines, a brand-new day.

Through every trial, we endure,
With love and grace, our path is sure.
Together strong, we stand as one,
With God, our battles will be won.

God will lift us up again,
Through the fire, through the rain.
Hope’s not lost, we still believe,
America will rise and lead.

From the mountains to the sea,
Let faith restore our destiny.
We will rise, we won’t back down,
With God above, we wear the crown.

God will lift us up again,
Through the fire, through the rain.
Hope’s not lost, we still believe,
America will rise and lead.
